WEBVTT

00:00:01.117 --> 00:00:05.339
A canta xente de aquí lle gustaría vivir
ata ter polo menos 80 anos?

00:00:06.072 --> 00:00:07.269
Si.

00:00:07.571 --> 00:00:10.366
Penso que todos temos esta esperanza

00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:12.183
de vivir ata a vellez.

00:00:12.828 --> 00:00:14.914
Imos proxectarnos no futuro,

00:00:14.938 --> 00:00:16.498
nos "vostedes" futuros,

00:00:16.522 --> 00:00:19.375
e imos imaxinar que todos temos 85 anos.

00:00:19.894 --> 00:00:21.912
Agora mírense uns aos outros.

00:00:23.151 --> 00:00:26.683
Un de vostedes 
probablemente terá alzhéimer.

00:00:27.365 --> 00:00:29.413
(Risos)